asset.author: Hoover
asset.hookText: Hi RSS: We saw your review on Amazon.com. If your Air Pro is shutting off, it is probably clog. Since you just took it out of the box, we think it is probably because of the position of the dial. If the dial isn't placed completely in Floor or Hose mode, that could cause the vacuum to clog. Felicia put together this quick video for you to show you what I mean. Let us know if you need more help!
